id, \u201cDo not say: O Allah, fortify me from trials. Indeed, not one of you returns to his family and children but that it is included among the trials. Rather, say: O Allah, I seek refuge in you from trials\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11341,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/11\/khawarij-kharijite-quran-throats\/","url_meta":{"origin":19781,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Khawarij: Violent rebels recite Quran, but do not understand","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere will come a people from the east, who recite the Quran but it does not go beyond their throats. They will go out of the religion, just as an arrow pierces through its target, and they\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8048,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/13\/signs-hour-murder-family\/","url_meta":{"origin":19781,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Sign of the Hour is killing neighbors, family members","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Hour will not be established until a man kills his neighbor, his brother, and his father.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 118 Grade: Jayyid (